      "seed": 510016,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 610016,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "6. Read via Personal Server\n\nBuilder resolves user's servers.\nLaptop closed means use HPS.\nHPS verifies grant with DP RPC.\nHPS decrypts K_enc_HPS, fetches ciphertext, slices scope, logs access.\n\nUI meaning: Tool receives approved data.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "6. Read via Personal Server\n\nBuilder resolves user's servers.\nLaptop closed means use HPS.\nHPS verifies grant with DP RPC.\nHPS decrypts K_enc_HPS, fetches ciphertext, slices scope, logs access.\n\nUI meaning: Tool receives approved data.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 186
    },
