      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Preserve these invariants: master signature is not product auth; file key K is random per file; K is escrowed to multiple recipients; wallet address is the Vana subject; silent-sign is allowlisted; builders should target account.vana.org/OIDC; reads do not touch the wallet.",
